  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-customer-story=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6 flex-initial article-module__9eLiuW__content\">\n   <div class=\"rounded-[6px] p-2 bg-background-100 shadow-sm bg-clip-padding max-w-[900px] grid grid-cols-1 sm:border-l-0 sm:border-r-0 sm:rounded-none sm:border-[var(--guide-color)] sm:max-w-none sm:w-full mt-4 mb-6 max-w-[var(--article-max-width)]\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" width=\"900\" height=\"471\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic rounded-md border border-solid border-gray-200 image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F4JYtOIcxv7uaav9R9jn3Fo%2F3dda5b39211a0b6084341a0bf983c660%2FAWS-light.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F4JYtOIcxv7uaav9R9jn3Fo%2F3dda5b39211a0b6084341a0bf983c660%2FAWS-light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F4JYtOIcxv7uaav9R9jn3Fo%2F3dda5b39211a0b6084341a0bf983c660%2FAWS-light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Today we’re introducing native support for <a href=\"https://vercel.com/marketplace/aws\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/marketplace/aws\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">AWS</a> databases including Amazon Aurora PostgreSQL, Amazon Aurora DSQL, and Amazon DynamoDB on the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/marketplace/category/database\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/marketplace/category/database\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Vercel Marketplace</a>.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">This gives developers a direct path to provision and manage scalable, production-ready AWS databases from within the Vercel dashboard with no manual setup required, and:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__unorderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><b>One-click support</b> for creating a new AWS account, provisioning new AWS databases and linking them to your Vercel projects.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><b>Improved developer experience</b> with simplified region selection, secure credential handling, and unified monitoring of AWS database resources from Vercel.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><b>Automatic environment variable</b> for connection strings and credentials, securely stored within your Vercel project.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><b>Free starter plan</b> for new AWS customers, including <b>$100 in credits</b>, with deep links to manage or upgrade plans in the AWS console.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><b>And coming soon:</b> Provision databases into your existing AWS account, attach them to your projects, and access AWS databases directly inside <a href=\"https://v0.app\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://v0.app\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono);font-feature-settings:&quot;tnum&quot;\">v0</span></a>.</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper code-blo